            <title>[LU-14109] export --backup option is missing from lnetctl man page</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14109</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The lnetctl export &quot;&#8211;backup&quot; option is not described in the manpage.&lt;/p&gt;

